PrecisAuthority for the Canada Ports Corporation to grant two perpetual EASEMENTS to HYDRO-QUÉBEC for the installation, operation, repair, etc., of electrical power transmission lines under two strips of land situated at the PORT OF TROIS-RIVIÈRES which contain an area of some 344.4 m² and 74 m² respectively, in order to connect two of its tenants to the utility, namely Lauralco Inc. and Société québécoise d'assainissement des eaux.
